  "description": "This is one of our favorite air fryer recipes. Apart from marinating the chicken overnight, it doesn’t take a lot of time to prepare, and you could start eating while the second and third batches are still cooking. This is a perfect Monday dinner recipe (we usually buy a full chicken on Saturday, so we have marinated legs and wings ready to be fried on Monday).",
